{"tid":582583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★IT狗 力斥政府網站設計 5 宗罪！","createTime":"2018-03-06T10:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T16:15:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"980944cede27686120125646466a21355716809d","tid":582583,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:01:41.000Z","msg":"雖然每間企業當要裁員時，「IT 狗」定必首當其衝飯碗不保，但假如一間公司沒有好的「IT 狗」幫助建立 user friendly 的網站，一樣會令市民公憤。說的是有位真・IT 狗近日在 FB po 長文力斥政府網站的建立沒有邏輯可言，便用起來絕不 user friendly、垃垃圾圾乜乜乜，而在這篇文章的結論部分，更是《創世紀》許文彪上身，大呼「公平咩」，並有感：「政府果班PM，對上果班 vendor 呀，佢地識 programming 識 UX 咩？佢哋只係左手交右手，拎少少時間，判上判上判就不停係度賺大錢，咁叫公平咩！」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>政府網站出現的 5 宗罪：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1）無 config root domain<br />\n<br />\n政府網站竟沒有 DNS Record（網域名稱系統），覺得超級不合時宜之外，也認為 Pizza Hut 網站都不設 DNS Record，是因為跟隨了政府做法。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1910000/1910319/20170922_IT_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1910000%2F1910319%2F20170922_IT_02_600.jpg&h=a8b5634d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）想做網上預約但指去填 PDF 表格<br />\n<br />\n本身想做網上預約，但發現沒有按鈕可按之外，之後當發現有連結可做網上預約之際，此連結竟指去 PDF 表格頁面，並需要另行填寫及遞交。同時也不解指南 link 不是指導到預約頁面，要兜大圈才找到。（樓主表示黑人問號 ing）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1910000/1910319/20170922_IT_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1910000%2F1910319%2F20170922_IT_03_600.jpg&h=33102f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）Print / Save 按鈕不能用<br />\n<br />\n有一個不能用的 Print / Save 按鈕，又有何用呢？（樓主繼續黑人問號 ing）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1910000/1910319/20170922_IT_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1910000%2F1910319%2F20170922_IT_04_600.jpg&h=4788c6ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb34ca8097740e5370b248264a924576d8acc50f","tid":582583,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"4）Invalid Digital Signature<br />\n<br />\n政府 PDF 的簽名都可 invalid？不禁要懷疑政府網站的保安程度有多嚴密......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1910000/1910319/20170922_IT_05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1910000%2F1910319%2F20170922_IT_05_600.jpg&h=dc2d8ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5）政府部門網站沒有互認<br />\n<br />\n入境處、香港郵政網站沒用互認版，讓樓主大感困惑：「sign 嚟做乜 X？」，以及令他驚訝，何解一個網站漏洞，同樣也等於它的功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1910000/1910319/20170922_IT_06_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1910000%2F1910319%2F20170922_IT_06_600.jpg&h=abb35832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1910000/1910319/20170922_IT_07_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1910000%2F1910319%2F20170922_IT_07_600.jpg&h=3016145d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n質疑創科局存在價值<br />\n<br />\n當樓主發現一個政府網站都可以如此落後、不 user friendly 之時，某程度已曲線懷疑創科局的存在為何物之外，「香港有價值 183 億嘅創新及科技局 Innovation and Technology Bureau HK 呀嘛，聽日一定會好天嘅，我先唔會插香港政府啲 IT 廢呀。」，也同時直線抽擊政府 IT 狗垃圾到不能。「政府果班 PM，對上果班 vendor 呀，佢地識 programming 識 UX 咩？佢哋只係左手交右手，拎少少時間，判上判上判就不停係度賺大錢。」不知道大家又會否有這樣的看法呢？<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1910319/%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%8EIT%20%E7%8B%97%E5%8A%9B%E6%96%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%205%20%E5%AE%97%E7%BD%AA%EF%BC%81%E7%84%A1%20DNS%20Record%20%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%99%82%E5%AE%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1910319%2F%25E7%259C%259F%25EF%25BC%258EIT%2520%25E7%258B%2597%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AB%2599%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25205%2520%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25BD%25AA%25EF%25BC%2581%25E7%2584%25A1%2520DNS%2520Record%2520%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25AE%259C&d=AiK%2FvUy3SAFDSmMwJ3%2B8654f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1527b3e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1910319/%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%8EIT%20%E7%8B%97%E5%8A%9B%E6%96%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%205%20%E5%AE%97%E7%BD%AA%EF%BC%81%E7%84%A1%20DNS%20Record%20%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%99%82%E5%AE%9C</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"e70e00bc7def79ebbcb98d37d68cf689c90680f2","tid":582583,"uid":113626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好賴外判, 以前就算係直屬請人政府個網都係垃圾黎"},{"pid":"215591d8ef783528935801326e4e477d23fb05f9","tid":582583,"uid":51932,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"你幫政府整好，佢幫你宣傳點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba42e0e7464796f59dfbffb59bbe80cfc46a4462","tid":582583,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:08:09.000Z","msg":"有錢就一齊貪, 有bug就互傳"},{"pid":"d681884e76e815c6b5de4dcae664699128a11025","tid":582583,"uid":24660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"老貓做乜今日咁搶口"},{"pid":"7921c80803bd541beba5b143b1faee6c25902d37","tid":582583,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 500億創科真係得啖笑<br />\n攞嚟update系統算喇"},{"pid":"88e8d9c2e8205a52adfbf08bab52f6d337fd2f14","tid":582583,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7921c80803bd541beba5b143b1faee6c25902d37","tid":582583,"uid":